sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as Flutter App
    participant Auth as Firebase Auth
    participant FS as Firestore
    participant DB as Roles Collection
    
    User->>App: Enter Email & Password
    App->>Auth: signInWithEmailAndPassword()
    Auth-->>App: UserCredential
    
    alt Sign In Success
        App->>FS: Fetch user document (uid)
        FS-->>App: User data (roleId ref)
        App->>DB: Fetch role document
        DB-->>App: Role (admin/customer)
        
        alt Admin Role
            App->>App: Navigate to Admin Dashboard
        else Customer Role
            App->>App: Navigate to Home Screen
        end
        
        App->>User: Display authenticated UI
    else Sign In Failed
        Auth-->>App: FirebaseAuthException
        App->>User: Show localized error
    end
    
    User->>App: Request Sign Out
    App->>Auth: signOut()
    Auth-->>App: Success
    App->>App: Clear user state
    App->>User: Navigate to Sign In
    
    Note over App,Auth: Auth state listener triggers on all changes
    App->>Auth: authStateChanges() listener
    Auth-->>App: Auth state (null/user)
    App->>App: Handle route redirects
